  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Melffy God Mommy",
      "effect": "3+ Level 2 Beast monsters\nOnce per turn, you can also Xyz Summon \"Melffy God Mommy\" by using \"Melffy Mommy\" you control (transfer its materials). If this card is Special Summoned: You can add 1 \"Melffy\" Spell/Trap from your Deck or GY to your hand. Gains ATK equal to the combined ATK and DEF of all \"Melffy\" monsters attached to it. You can detach 5 materials from this card; return all cards your opponent controls to the hand.",
      "official": false
    },
    "ja": {
